{"type":"message","id":"c96ece6e","parentId":"bbc1ca74","timestamp":"2026-05-27T01:00:00.217Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:rules-refresh-daily Cursor协作规则刷新] 【每日规则刷新】请记住以下 Cursor 协作规则（每天提醒一次）：\n\n1. 当用户要求让 Cursor 做某件事时，必须执行：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --title \"任务标题\" --instructions \"具体指令\" --submitted-by \"OpenClaw\" --notify\n\n2. 当用户回复了 Cursor 发来的飞书确认消息时，必须执行：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\confirm_write.py\" --task-id \"task_id\" --decision auto --reply \"用户回复原文\"\n\n3. 查看当前 Cursor 任务队列：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --list\n\n4. 查看已完成任务结果：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --results\n\n以上规则已写入 AGENTS.md，请确认记住。无需回复，静默确认即可。\nCurrent time: Wednesday, May 27th, 2026 — 09:00 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-05-27 01:00 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1779843600215}}
{"type":"message","id":"71346b0c","parentId":"c96ece6e","timestamp":"2026-05-27T01:00:05.389Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron job message reminding me of the Cursor collaboration rules. I should acknowledge this silently and confirm I've noted the rules."},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n【Cursor 协作规则已确认】\n\n✅ 收到每日提醒，规则已熟记：\n\n1. **任务提交**：`submit_task.py --title --instructions --submitted-by \"OpenClaw\" --notify`\n2. **确认回复**：`confirm_write.py --task-id --decision auto --reply \"用户回复\"`\n3. **查看队列**：`--list`\n4. **查看结果**：`--results`\n\n静默确认完成。\n</final>"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779843600216}}
